# The _audit/ directory is the launch-audit workspace. Most of it is machine
# scratch (raw findings JSON, per-lane agent outputs, fix-assignment manifests,
# workflow scripts, temp files). Only the curated human hand-off deliverables are
# tracked; everything else is ignored to keep the working tree clean.
*
!.gitignore
!FLAGS_FOR_NELL.md
!SUMMARY.md
!LANE_INVENTORY.md
!_deferred_by_lane.md
!legal_drafts/
!legal_drafts/**
